819
00:52:07.667 --> 00:52:10.002
<i>to ruin this city's
Christmas spirit.</i>

820
00:52:10.002 --> 00:52:13.172
<i>Not mine. I love that tree.</i>

821
00:52:14.131 --> 00:52:17.510
What a genius.

