Why did you bring me here?

851
00:54:31.769 --> 00:54:32.687
Whoa.

852
00:54:37.316 --> 00:54:38.776
Haven't you figured it out?

853
00:54:38.776 --> 00:54:42.279
We needed to get the Bat
out of Gotham.

854
00:54:42.279 --> 00:54:47.868
However. it appears
a much smaller Bat
