I'm not a baby.

882
00:56:12.161 --> 00:56:14.455
Indeed. You are not a baby.

883
00:56:14.455 --> 00:56:17.041
You have been alive
for eight years.

884
00:56:17.041 --> 00:56:18.751
And four days.

