00:57:31.407 --> 00:57:32.491
It's okay.

907
00:57:32.491 --> 00:57:36.036
Just promise to give one
to your father
when you next see him.

908
00:57:36.954 --> 00:57:39.582
Yeah. I kind of owe him
one anyway.

