00:58:42.144 --> 00:58:45.022
<i>I never used
those words exactly.</i>

921
00:58:45.022 --> 00:58:46.357
Joker!

922
00:58:46.357 --> 00:58:49.109
<i>Oh. he may be obnoxious.
and he certainly acts
