00:59:59.346 --> 01:00:01.181
This plan better work.

951
01:00:01.181 --> 01:00:02.599
{\an8}All right. pipsqueak.

952
01:00:02.599 --> 01:00:04.101
Come and get it.

953
01:00:13.360 --> 01:00:14.653
Yeah!

