We're almost there.

966
01:01:10.959 --> 01:01:12.669
Got room for one more?

967
01:01:12.669 --> 01:01:14.880
Huh? For such a little kid.

968
01:01:14.880 --> 01:01:17.383
you sure are a pain
in the neck.

969
