01:02:06.723 --> 01:02:09.226
Let go. kid.
You'll kill us both.

977
01:02:09.226 --> 01:02:10.727
Give it to me! Give it to me!

978
01:02:10.727 --> 01:02:11.728
Give it to me!

979
01:02:11.728 --> 01:02:14.857
